/France\", \"score\": 0.9990470015341211, \"rank\": 0.0007211242846862089, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the father of Sequana, the goddess who is connected to the river, the Seine.\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2185, \"end\": 2192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sequana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sequana\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sequana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sequana\"}, {\"begin\": 2241, \"end\": 2246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.354853124423095e-14, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The idea was to have a pagan celebration connected to the gods of Olympus.\\\"\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2323, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2314, \"end\": 2321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\", \"score\": 0.9999999796837076, \"rank\": 2.0315421428412948e-08, \"text\": \"Olympus\", \"types\": [\"Q8502\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You will never find in me a desire to mock and denigrate anyone.\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2390, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted to make a ceremony that repairs, that reconciles, and also that reaffirms the values \\u200b\\u200bof our Republic: liberty-equality-fraternity,\\\" Jolly continued.\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2550, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"BIDEN, HARRIS CALLED OUT BY RELIGIOUS GROUPS FOR STAYING SILENT ON 'INSULTING' OLYMPICS LAST SUPPER DRAG PARODY  Trump said if he were at the 2028 Los Angeles Olympic Games and could influence the organiz